When you start the application for the first time, you will need to activate it. There are two ways in which you can do this:

Use my mobile number

- this option enables you to activate the app using your own mobile phone number. When you first activate your number, you will be given a PIN and it\'s very IMPORTANT that you write it down.

- if you wish to use your mobile phone number on another device you will be asked for PIN in the process

IMPORTANT: This process will send one SMS to verify your mobile phone number!

Give me number

- if you decide to go with this option, you will be assigned a number. This option does NOT send SMS.

If you wish to use a different number after you\'ve been assigned one, you will need to uninstall and then reinstall application.
